headline: Deckers Bets Big on Wholesale: Will HOKA and UGG Sustain the Pace?
summary: DECK leans into wholesale growth as HOKA and UGG fuel fourth-quarter gains, aiming for a 50-50 split with DTC in fiscal 2026.
